      %p.font-weight-bold
        Current Employment
      %p
        I am a Senior Engineer with
        = link_to "Comcast’s", "https://www.xfinity.com/", target: "_blank"
        Technology and Product Development organization (T&#38;P).
      %p
        I am a member of the Applications Management Tools Team consisting of six Developers (including myself), a Manager and a Business Analyst. We’re building Configuration Management Database systems and Asset Management systems that track configuration and network topology information for the 7000+ Applications and 500K+ Devices used within T&#38;P.
      %p
        Our development stack includes
        = link_to "Ruby on Rails", "http://rubyonrails.org/", target: "_blank"
        4.x and 5.1. Front-end technology includes
        = link_to "jQuery", "http://jquery.com/", target: "_blank"
        and
        = link_to "Twitter Bootstrap", "https://getbootstrap.com/", target: "_blank"
        , and our backend databases are
        = link_to "MySQL", "https://www.mysql.com/", target: "_blank"
        &#44;
        = link_to "MongoDB", "https://www.mongodb.com/", target: "_blank"
        and
        = link_to "Oracle", "https://www.oracle.com/database/index.html", target: "_blank"
        &#46; We do a lot of
        = link_to "API", "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Application_programming_interface", target: "_blank"
        work as we talk to over a dozen databases within the T&#38;P community.
        = link_to "Version Control", "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Version_control", target: "_blank"
        and
        = link_to "Continuous Integration", "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Continuous_integration", target: "_blank"
        of the Rails code base are handled by
        =link_to "Git", "https://git-scm.com/", target: "_blank"
        and
        =link_to "Jenkins", "https://jenkins.io/index.html", target: "_blank"
        &#46;
      %p
        We use
        = link_to "puma", "http://puma.io/", target: "_blank"
        &#44;
        = link_to "nginx", "https://www.nginx.com/", target: "_blank"
